OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.DESCRIPTION: This selector shows all the available products
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HELP: This selector shows all the available products

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner not filtered by default by customer/vendor
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT distinct bp.name as name,bp.id as bpid, bp.searchKey as value, bp.creditLimit - bp.creditUsed as creditAvailable, bp.creditUsed as creditUsed, COALESCE(contact.name, usercontact.name) as contactname, COALESCE(contact.id, usercontact.id) as contactid, bploc.name as locationname, bploc.id as locationid, bp.customer as customer, bp.vendor as vendor, bp.lifetimeRevenueToDate as income FROM BusinessPartner bp left join bp.businessPartnerLocationList bploc left join bploc.locationAddress loc left join bploc.aDUserList contact left join loc.region region left join bp.aDUserList usercontact with usercontact.partnerAddress.id is null where @additional_filters@ and bp.summaryLevel = false and bp.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product Complete
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "( (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'800051\', \'800052\', \'800096\') and e.product.production = true and e.stocked = false) or (\'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' in (\'170\') and e.product.stocked = true) or \'"+OB.getWindowId()+"\' not in (\'800051\', \'800052\', \'800096\',\'170\'))"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner with contact and location
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT bp.name as name,bp.id as bpid, bp.searchKey as value, bp.creditLimit - bp.creditUsed as creditAvailable, bp.creditUsed as creditUsed, bp.customer as customer, bp.vendor as vendor, bp.businessPartnerCategory.name as category FROM BusinessPartner bp where @additional_filters@ and bp.summaryLevel = false and bp.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Org_no_org_access
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: ((org.client = @ad_client_id@ and (select r.id from ADRole r where r.manual = 'Y' and r.id = @ad_role_id@) = @ad_role_id@) or (org.id in (select org2 from ADRole r2 left join r2.aDRoleOrganizationList ol left join ol.organization org2 where r2.id = @ad_role_id@)))
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select org.id as orgid, org.name as name, org.searchKey as value from Organization org where @additional_filters@

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Element Value
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.active = true and exists (select 1 from FinancialMgmtAcctSchemaElement c where c.accountingSchema.id=@inpcAcctschemaId@ and c.accountingElement.id = e.accountingElement.id)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: ProductSimple
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: if (OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId')){ " pl.salesPriceList = " + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " AND c.id = '" + OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId') + "'" }
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select p.searchKey as searchKey, p.id as id, plv as priceListVersion, plv.name as priceListVersionName, c.id as currency, pp.priceLimit as priceLimit, p.name as productName,p.uOM as uOM, pp.standardPrice as standardPrice, pp.listPrice as netListPrice, pl.salesPriceList as salesPriceList from PricingProductPrice pp join pp.product p join pp.priceListVersion plv join plv.priceList pl left join pl.currency c where @additional_filters@

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner with contact and location
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT distinct bp.name as name,bp.id as bpid, bp.searchKey as value, bp.creditLimit - bp.creditUsed as creditAvailable, bp.creditUsed as creditUsed, COALESCE(contact.name, usercontact.name) as contactname, COALESCE(contact.id, usercontact.id) as contactid, bploc.name as locationname, bploc.id as locationid, bp.customer as customer, bp.vendor as vendor, bp.lifetimeRevenueToDate as income FROM BusinessPartner bp left join bp.businessPartnerLocationList bploc with bploc.active=true left join bploc.locationAddress loc with loc.active = true left join bploc.aDUserList contact with contact.active=true left join loc.region region left join bp.aDUserList usercontact with usercontact.partnerAddress.id is null and usercontact.active=true where @additional_filters@ and bp.summaryLevel = false and bp.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: On hand warehouse
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "( (" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = true and w.id in (select ow.warehouse.id from OrganizationWarehouse ow where ow.warehouse.id = w.id and ow.organization.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpadOrgId') + "\' )) or (" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = false))"
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select w.id as id, w.name as name from Warehouse w where @additional_filters@
